        <div class="profile-photo">
            <img src="~/Images/CVicon.png" alt="Profile Photo" class="profile-img" />
        </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="cv-section about">
            <h3>About Me</h3>
            <p>Get to know who I am beyond the CV...my background, passion for technology, personal story, and what drives me to build digital solutions.</p>
            <a asp-action="About" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="cv-section experience">
            <h3>Experience</h3>
            <p>Explore my professional history: roles I've held and the responsibilities I’ve handled.</p>
            <br />
            <br />
            <a asp-action="Experience" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="cv-section education">
            <h3>Education</h3>
            <p>A look into my academic journey, schools, degrees, certifications, and relevant coursework that have shaped my technical expertise.</p>
            <a asp-action="Education" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="cv-section skills">
            <h3>Skills</h3>
            <p>An overview of my technical stack including programming languages, frameworks, tools, and soft skills that power my work.</p>
            <a asp-action="Skills" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="cv-section projects">
            <h3>Projects</h3>
            <p>View a collection of personal, academic, freelance projects, and what I learned during each build.</p>
            <a asp-action="Projects" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </section>

        <section class="cv-section contact">
            <h3>Contact</h3>
            <p>Need to reach me? Whether it's work inquiries, collaboration, or just saying hi. Here’s how you can connect.</p>
            <br />
            <a asp-action="Contact" asp-controller="Home" class="btn">Reach Out</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="cv-footer">
       Thank you! For getting to know me.
    </footer>
</div>
